1
00:00:58,046 --> 00:01:01,022
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,022 --> 00:01:02,992
=Episode 21=

3
00:01:02,992 --> 00:01:07,014
(Clouds Part, Truth Rises)

4
00:01:07,599 --> 00:01:09,000
If my deduction holds,

5
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,359
it's all

6
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:13,640
the family head's design.

7
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:23,519
Master.

8
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:26,439
Where have you been at this hour?

9
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:31,359
The body at the temple implicates
Master Chaosheng. I went to handle it.

10
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:36,200
How did it go?

11
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,680
I've replaced the pouch
with a similar one.

12
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:41,560
The officials won't link this
to Master Chaosheng.

13
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:44,879
I'll find the real culprit quickly
to clear Master Chaosheng's name.

14
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:50,400
Yuluo, the truth about the massacre
of Qin Yuheng's family is with me,

15
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,079
not the Xuanji Pavilion.

16
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:56,840
I can overlook your intrusion
into the Pavilion.

17
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,439
If you want the truth,

18
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:03,680
come to me after you uncover
the mastermind behind this.

19
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,560
That secret letter

20
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,480
was from you?

21
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:09,560
No, I received a secret letter too.

22
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,680
(Something happened to Yuluo.)

23
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:14,400
(She learned from a secret letter)

24
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:18,280
(she's Qin Xiang, Qin Yuheng's daughter,
the sole survivor of the Qin massacre,)

25
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:23,240
(and that you were
involved in that slaughter.)

26
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:28,039
(The letter says
you received a secret letter)

27
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:31,840
and learned that I had a hand
in the Qin family's massacre.

28
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,240
Last night, we got separated.

29
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:44,000
I couldn't find you afterward.

30
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,680
Thank you for clearing my name.

31
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:50,840
It's nothing.

32
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:56,120
Is there anything else?

33
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,280
Where are you going?

34
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:04,560
To investigate Xuanwu's disappearance
by the Pavilion Master's order.

35
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,199
I understood your meaning last night.

36
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:10,919
If you want to see fireworks,

37
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:13,039
after you return
from the investigation...

38
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:13,539
Dear.

39
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:40,199
Dear, come back early.

40
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:45,879
It won't be long.
Take good care of yourself.

41
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:53,159
Whether the family head
is the mastermind or not,

42
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:55,319
you've passed his test for now.

43
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:01,280
I'll wait here for you
in the Fufeng Pavilion.

44
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:27,720
When I return, it'll be our wedding day.

45
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:31,279
You must prepare well.

46
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:58,120
(If you want to know who framed you,)

47
00:04:58,279 --> 00:05:00,279
(go to the Fufeng Pavilion tonight.)

48
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:05,360
(Then all will be revealed.)

49
00:05:07,904 --> 00:05:10,624
(Fufeng Pavilion)

50
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:26,120
Why isn't Yuluo here today?

51
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,399
Father sent her on an errand.

52
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,079
To find Xuanwu?

53
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:46,879
I wanted to discuss
wedding details with her.

54
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:49,160
Why did Father send her
on an errand now?

55
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:54,680
It's fine. After she returns,

56
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,639
I'll tell her you came for her.

57
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,920
You're remarkably composed.

58
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,879
Had Xuanwu succeeded,

59
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:05,639
it'd hurt Yuluo's chance
to become the Pavilion Master.

60
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:09,560
Don't you want to do something for her?

61
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:13,759
What do you think I should do?

62
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:39,079
If you like her, fight for her

63
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,600
and help her seize the Pavilion.

64
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:47,360
Do you really think the Pavilion
is what Yuluo truly wants?

65
00:06:47,759 --> 00:06:49,519
Even though we're all in the Gu family,

66
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:51,879
you've had no real connection
with her these past years.

67
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:56,079
She'd rather marry a stranger like you
for the Pavilion Master position.

68
00:06:56,399 --> 00:06:58,920
Doesn't that show how important
that position is to her?

69
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,800
And you, you've done nothing,

70
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:10,839
but why do you get everything

71
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:12,839
just because Father said so?

72
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,560
When did you...?

73
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,600
This is Laughing Netherworld.

74
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:42,120
No, I won't let you
laugh your way to the netherworld.

75
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:44,512
This is more potent.

76
00:07:44,512 --> 00:07:46,000
It has no antidote.

77
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:48,639
It will kill you
through excruciating pain.

78
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:51,920
It will invade every part of your body,

79
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:54,319
making you die in agony.

80
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:57,480
Who exactly are you?

81
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,360
How did you come back?

82
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:04,160
No matter how many times
you come back to life,

83
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,360
I killed you once.

84
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:08,519
I can kill you a second time.

85
00:08:14,759 --> 00:08:15,879
"A second time"?

86
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:20,560
Yes, the previous one was killed by me.

87
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,399
It was you.

88
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:25,319
The wolf pit.

89
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,540
Yes.

90
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,879
It was me.

91
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,679
What is this?

92
00:08:43,639 --> 00:08:44,360
Worthless.

93
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,480
It's for my wife.

94
00:08:48,039 --> 00:08:49,639
"Wife"? You don't deserve it.

95
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,919
Someone! Throw him into the wolf pit!

96
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:21,000
I had him thrown into the wolf pit

97
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:23,799
and watched with my own eyes
as wolves tore his body apart.

98
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:26,600
No matter which of you is real

99
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,120
or how many Gu Zhaoxi exist,

100
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:32,320
I'll eliminate every last one of them.

101
00:09:32,799 --> 00:09:35,519
You are siblings.
Why must you be so ruthless?

102
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:45,679
How could you...

103
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,200
How could I come back?

104
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:53,120
Pity. I never left,
waiting to draw you out.

105
00:10:00,399 --> 00:10:01,519
You weren't poisoned.

106
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:03,720
Obviously.

107
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:22,000
If you had a change of heart

108
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,840
and this were only a sleeping drug,

109
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:26,480
we could still mend things.

110
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:30,320
But sadly, you showed no regret.

111
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:34,360
- You've only gotten worse.
- You threw your brother into the pit

112
00:10:34,639 --> 00:10:35,759
and watched him die.

113
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,840
Later, learning Chaosheng
also hired a killer,

114
00:10:39,279 --> 00:10:42,080
you plotted to kill the killer
and pin it all on him.

115
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,279
Too bad

116
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:46,320
you didn't know
he was seen hiring the killer

117
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:48,240
and uncovered the whole truth.

118
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:02,360
I never imagined
you'd go to such lengths

119
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:04,840
just to frame me for everything.

120
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:10,440
Get her.

121
00:11:42,559 --> 00:11:44,159
The poison in me came from him.

122
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,799
And you still want to protect him?

123
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:06,559
Even now, won't you turn back?

124
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:07,919
Wenshuang.

125
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:20,559
You... when?

126
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:22,039
Long before,

127
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:25,152
I asked you to find Physician Qin,

128
00:12:25,152 --> 00:12:27,008
(but I got ambushed
at the Lantern Festival.)

129
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:30,519
When was Zhaoxi found?

130
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:32,759
Two days ago.

131
00:12:36,799 --> 00:12:39,480
I was lured to Zuixian Building
in Xuanji's name,

132
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,039
but thinking back,

133
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:44,120
the first person I saw
at the door was you.

134
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:45,240
Yuluo.

135
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,600
He invited us here and ditched us?

136
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:49,159
Exactly.

137
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,679
I didn't want to believe it,

138
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:55,519
but

139
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:59,639
that bracelet made me truly suspicious.

140
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,279
Investigate

141
00:13:11,399 --> 00:13:13,480
where Gu Wenshuang was

142
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:17,399
on the day Master Zhaoxi was attacked.

143
00:13:17,759 --> 00:13:21,159
My bracelet broke years ago.

144
00:13:21,639 --> 00:13:24,240
When you gave me a new one,
I found it strange.

145
00:13:25,279 --> 00:13:28,000
I thought you'd simply seen it
by chance in Mobei

146
00:13:28,279 --> 00:13:31,279
and remembered that old story.

147
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:35,440
That changed when I saw
the bracelet found with Zhaoxi.

148
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,759
You secretly returned early

149
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:42,080
and pinned the killing on the bandits
who killed the Crown Prince, Yin Zhou,

150
00:13:42,759 --> 00:13:44,320
trying to cover your tracks.

151
00:13:45,039 --> 00:13:46,039
You didn't stop.

152
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:50,799
After learning Chaosheng
had hired a killer, you killed that one

153
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:52,799
to cover up Zhaoxi's death.

154
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:56,240
Unsure if he was truly dead,

155
00:13:56,759 --> 00:13:59,759
you even bribed people
to check the remains as a cover,

156
00:14:01,639 --> 00:14:05,600
so you could slip in dressed as a beggar
and examine the remains yourself.

157
00:14:21,399 --> 00:14:24,480
For this, you wouldn't hesitate
to kill those people.

158
00:14:24,759 --> 00:14:25,919
But you didn't know

159
00:14:26,519 --> 00:14:29,600
your cleverness exposed you.

160
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:34,080
Why are there so many people today?

161
00:14:37,519 --> 00:14:38,159
By the way,

162
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:42,080
you used Xuanji's Laughing Netherworld
to kill Leng Yan.

163
00:14:42,639 --> 00:14:43,840
You poisoned the family head.

164
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:47,600
And now, you're disguised as Xuanji,
making another move against Zhaoxi.

165
00:14:48,039 --> 00:14:50,000
Why have you become like this?

166
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:20,799
But why did you kill Physician Qin
and Zuixian Building's owner?

167
00:15:21,559 --> 00:15:26,039
Just because I said I hoped
Physician Qin could cure Zhaoxi?

168
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,100
No.

169
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,799
You knew I got that secret letter,

170
00:15:44,919 --> 00:15:47,679
and you knew I'd start
suspecting the Gu family,

171
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:52,240
so you killed them.

172
00:15:52,639 --> 00:15:54,440
I did all this for you!

173
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,639
What makes him better than me?

174
00:15:58,639 --> 00:16:02,039
- Great!
- Great!

175
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:03,000
Again!

176
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,279
- Great!
- Great!

177
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:18,480
I've been your fighting partner,
just because you were obsessed with it.

178
00:16:19,759 --> 00:16:21,159
For you, I searched for lanterns,

179
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:24,279
I fought for the family head position,

180
00:16:25,919 --> 00:16:28,960
and I even betrayed the whole world!

181
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,360
See this bracelet?

182
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:41,919
For ten years, I've worn it
every single day.

183
00:16:44,559 --> 00:16:46,799
I can give you anything you want.

184
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,519
But you?

185
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:52,200
You won't even look at me.

186
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,840
Why?

187
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:08,480
I never wanted any of this.

188
00:17:09,759 --> 00:17:11,359
Your sincerity is commendable.

189
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:14,960
But have you truly asked what she wants?

190
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:18,440
I want a blade I hold in my own hands,

191
00:17:19,119 --> 00:17:21,039
not power borrowed from another.

192
00:17:23,799 --> 00:17:25,160
Are you connected

193
00:17:27,759 --> 00:17:29,079
to the Pavilion's Heaven tasks?

194
00:17:30,039 --> 00:17:33,079
Was the family head's poison your doing?

195
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:36,079
What is your connection to Gu Xuanwu?

196
00:17:38,839 --> 00:17:39,799
I didn't.

197
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:43,759
I didn't poison Father.

198
00:17:46,559 --> 00:17:49,079
Who commanded you to do all this?

199
00:17:54,039 --> 00:17:55,480
If I don't say,

200
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,359
could you then

201
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:03,160
never, ever forget me?

202
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,480
The Heaven task matter is resolved.

203
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,480
The mastermind behind it all...

204
00:18:34,640 --> 00:18:36,519
Chief He, please.

205
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,400
Get lost!

206
00:18:40,359 --> 00:18:41,759
I'll walk myself.

207
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,864
How do you know about the investigation?

208
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,240
No.

209
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:04,359
You know martial arts.

210
00:19:05,119 --> 00:19:06,160
You're not Zhaoxi.

211
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:09,079
Who exactly are you?

212
00:19:39,039 --> 00:19:42,920
Yesterday's glory is gone today.

213
00:19:44,240 --> 00:19:48,599
The dream of power
has vanished into the clouds.

214
00:19:50,359 --> 00:19:54,240
I served with all my heart,

215
00:19:56,400 --> 00:20:00,720
but now, I'm left to wait for death.

216
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:05,200
Cold chains cast a solitary shadow.

217
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:12,920
The setting sun casts
its last glow through the window.

218
00:20:16,079 --> 00:20:20,039
I've felt the world's coldness.

219
00:20:20,359 --> 00:20:25,480
Heaven decides my journey's end.

220
00:21:01,342 --> 00:21:06,405
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

221
00:21:06,942 --> 00:21:12,263
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

222
00:21:12,830 --> 00:21:19,458
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

223
00:21:19,458 --> 00:21:24,222
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

224
00:21:24,222 --> 00:21:26,558
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

225
00:21:26,558 --> 00:21:33,258
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

226
00:21:33,258 --> 00:21:40,030
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

227
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:47,166
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

228
00:21:47,166 --> 00:21:51,550
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

229
00:21:51,550 --> 00:21:54,174
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

230
00:21:54,174 --> 00:22:00,808
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

231
00:22:00,808 --> 00:22:07,358
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

232
00:22:07,358 --> 00:22:14,482
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

233
00:22:14,572 --> 00:22:18,942
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

234
00:22:18,942 --> 00:22:21,650
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

235
00:22:21,650 --> 00:22:27,550
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

236
00:22:28,190 --> 00:22:34,178
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪
